  title="SPLITDO Token Presale | Blockchain Bill Splitting on Solana"
  description={`Join the SPLITDO token presale at ${formattedPrice}. Split bills with crypto on Solana blockchain. Lightning-fast settlements, near-zero fees. 100M supply, presale live now.`}
